=== ROS 2 Compile ===
$ cd ~/ros2_ws
$ ament build
OR
$ ament build --only-packages adlink_ros2

== ROS 2&1 Bridge ===
#Method-1 (rosparam)
$ roscore
$ rosparam set /topics "[{'topic':neonj_poses, 'type':geometry_msgs/PoseArray}]" 
$ ros2 run ros1_bridge parameter_bridge
$ ros2 run adlink_ros2 pose_array_pub
$ rostopic list 
(now you can echo "/neonj_poses", like: $ rostopic echo /neonj_poses)

#Method-2 (roslaunch)
$ roslaunch adlink_test PoseArray_Test.launch 
$ ros2 run ros1_bridge parameter_bridge
$ ros2 run adlink_ros2 pose_array_pub
$ rostopic list 
$ rostopic echo /neonj_poses
